Title: What Happened to You, Annalise?
Writer: Peter Nowalk (created by), J.C. Lee, Erika Harrison (story editor)
Actors: Viola Davis, Billy Brown, Alfred Enoch, Jack Falahee
Plot: Weeks after Wes shot Annalise, he and the rest of the Keating 5 deal with the ramifications of that night as Annalise works toward recovery.
